title: If you bought a OnePlus One, you have a chance to win a OnePlus 10 Pro for free; here’s how
content:
The OnePlus One was a big deal for the Android community back in 2014, and it helped launch a brand that has since become a pretty big player in the mobile space. Now, with the launch of the OnePlus 10 Pro, owners of the original OnePlus One are getting a shot at a free phone.
